title: back to the ocean
info:
hey global chipluverz!
After my trip to holland (zeeland)
my head is full cheesyness which needs
to be filled in +- 50kb .it container.

So I thought about the food, the girls
the ocean and other fine specials holland
is so famous for ;) and created this
"hymn" for my memories... yayz
Cheesy track, cheesy comment.

So turn up the volume, loop it a few
times, to get the "lekker" ko0x
flavor.
